{"tid":1133757,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"【向滷蛋花生致敬】淫亂的復仇者聯盟","createTime":"2019-05-01T10:13:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-03T19:24:52.000Z","uid":54337,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"5de16e9192b41a94d600c4cfb84c4eb75e57261c","tid":1133757,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T10:13:08.000Z","msg":"前言：<br />\n<br />\n我上高登，睇過好多滷蛋花生嘅咸故。<br />\n滷蛋花生係我偶像。<br />\n7年前，滷蛋花生作左個咸故*，<br />\n屌左復仇者1嘅黑寡婦。<br />\n<br />\n人面不知何處，綠水依舊東流。<br />\n<br />\n眨下眼，復仇者已經endgame，<br />\n我睹物思人，諗起我偶像滷蛋花生。<br />\n<br />\n所以我決定寫這個故仔，<br />\n向我偶像致敬。<br />\n<br />\n* <a href=\"https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=3747333&amp;&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D3747333%26%26page%3D1&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgEFScv4UPbHgCWRxxYzHlmUY%3D&h=1aa301ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=3747333&amp;&amp;page=1</a>"},{"pid":"d2f0f948c74c6725cf3b6ac1463bf53a6d430772","tid":1133757,"uid":207792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T10:35:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />lm"},{"pid":"352a19f7c9825db73ae451f77b61b935a3f291c1","tid":1133757,"uid":101253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T10:41:22.000Z","msg":"快  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c69f814a53ec4a88363d2d26f7349b1f38a0673f","tid":1133757,"uid":54337,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T10:48:34.000Z","msg":"第一章：加入神盾局<br />\n<br />\n我叫樓夢紅，係個30歲嘅廢柴窮撚。<br />\n<br />\n一直幫李嘉誠打工，在尖沙咀中港城嘅屈臣氏做執倉，人工有萬四。唉，陰鳩功。<br />\n<br />\n有一日，我在廣東道，遇到一個道士同一個高僧。兩條友瘋瘋癲癲，爛衫爛勢，結伴一齊，喺條街上面，鳩下鳩下，遊離朗蕩。<br />\n<br />\n兩條友見到我，嘻嘻哈哈，話我額有朝天骨，眼中有靈光，仙人托世，神仙下凡，仲話要收我為徒。<br />\n<br />\n我睬佢都有味，轉身想走。點知兩條友突然伸手捉住我，向上一跳。我凌空消失左。<br />\n<br />\n當我擘大眼，就見到一個古怪地方。<br />\n<img src=\"http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20171031/88ca612dc2194cc89732222a27a260c4.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F20171031%2F88ca612dc2194cc89732222a27a260c4.jpeg&h=0edbe425&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n眼前一片雲海，霧氣不過膝。人處其中，如騰雲駕霧。<br />\n<br />\n道士高僧企喺我面前。<br />\n道士自稱渺渺真人。<br />\n高僧自稱茫茫大士。<br />\n我身處嘅地方，叫太虛幻境。<br />\n<br />\n兩條友相視一笑，念咒語，展幻術，就將畢生功力傳比我。<br />\n我屌。就係咁樣，我無啦啦識幻術，亦做左幻術大師。<br />\n<br />\n我識幻術之後，即時劈炮。<br />\n講真，身懷絕技，仲同李老闆做奴隸咩？<br />\n<br />\n之後，我用幻術，偷呃拐騙，呃飲呃食，R下春袋又一日，簡直快樂過神仙。<br />\n<br />\n有日，我坐喺太興飲奶茶。<br />\n突然，有個穿皮褸嘅黑人坐我對面。<br />\n<br />\n我打個突。香港地成30幾度，仲著皮褸？都癡撚線<br />\n定睛一看，原來係神盾局局長 nick fury。<br />\n屌你老母，而家拍廣告呀？"},{"pid":"78beeb878b09100c0538106979fb9b14c1f7c805","tid":1133757,"uid":52793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T11:01:33.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"0c02fdeefaade59263654e06fe6ff1bccd7e072d","tid":1133757,"uid":72777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T11:08:16.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d15efbfb40f774852c24e66696f95bdff249b9b","tid":1133757,"uid":207702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T11:28:55.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"18312c5bdda5897a1a7f1c4fd022a17e63a81def","tid":1133757,"uid":216519,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T11:32:32.000Z","msg":"向老強致敬姐係爛尾？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90c7aa1fc71fa33f419ed9413e3868afc69db4f6","tid":1133757,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T11:53:09.000Z","msg":"局長一直直視我，唔閪出聲。<br />\n我同佢death air左一陣。<br />\n<br />\n講真，一個單眼嘅黑鬼，帶住眼罩，凶神惡煞咁望鳩住你，我雖然識幻術，身懷絕技，但個心難免有點淆青。<br />\n<br />\n局長揚一揚眉，向我道：「樓夢紅，港男，窮撚一個，原本做屈臣氏執倉。<br />\n有一日，你喺尖沙咀廣東道，識到兩個太虛幻境嘅神仙，茫茫大士同渺渺真人，收你為徒，教識你幻術。<br />\n之後，你就用幻術，偷呃拐騙，例如：憑空出現銀行金庫偷錢，之後憑空消失閃人。<br />\n你每次都唔貪心，只偷取小量銀紙。<br />\n由於損失金額太小，所以銀行普遍都唔報警。<br />\n你條仆街仔睇中呢點，所以長偷長有。」<br />\n<br />\n我聞言，大吃一驚，幾乎屎都標埋，竟然連我兩位神仙師父個花朵外號都查得出。<br />\n好野。唔係等閒之輩。<br />\n<br />\n我個心跳到發發聲，但故作鎮定，道：<br />\n「神仙，你講乜春野呀？<br />\n仲有呀，幻術？大佬，而家21世紀，你幾廿歲人仲信呢味野？<br />\n頭先你話我犯法？有咩證據先，老細？」<br />\n<br />\n局長唔出聲，於皮褸中，取出一部手機，按兩下掣，就show左幾張圖出嚟，全部都係我用幻術呃飲呃食嘅相，包括銀行金庫偷錢嘅cctv片段。<br />\n<br />\n局長幽幽道：「我係神盾局局長nick fury。這樣相同cctv短片，夠你踎赤柱十年八年。」<br />\n之後佢話口乾，叫侍應，點左杯太興奶茶，繼續道：<br />\n「Dr strange 識魔法；緋紅女巫 wanda 亦識魔法。<br />\n我親眼見到，唔到我唔信。<br />\n你嘅幻術，出神入化。論威力，絕對比得上dr strange同 wanda，我相信你嘅能力。<br />\n而且我對太虛幻境，他媽的好有興趣」<br />\n<br />\n下午3點，油塘大本型太興，人山人海。<br />\n如果我用幻術，隊冧黑鬼局長，或者憑空消失閃人，老老實實，真係易過借火。<br />\n但實在太多人在場，個撚個都睇到，我一定黃哂。<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母，死黑鬼。<br />\n無法，唯有見步行步。<br />\n<br />\n我問：「你想點？」<br />\n局長奸笑答：「我想你加入神盾局復仇者聯盟」<br />\n<br />\n聞言，我幾乎把口中的太興奶茶，噴撚到周圍都係。"},{"pid":"ebace42efac1253b027129968621ae190fe289a1","tid":1133757,"uid":14541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T11:57:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />lm"},{"pid":"8bef7b5ea8e0d41061e023ffb5051ea72cbe99bd","tid":1133757,"uid":54337,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T12:58:27.000Z","msg":"我認真問：「如果我唔加入呢？」<br />\n局長冷笑答：「兩個字：坐監。」<br />\n唉。加入咪加入囉，屌你老母。我好撚唔情願。<br />\n<br />\n都唔知坐左幾多個鐘頭飛機，左搖右搖，左轉右轉，山長水又遠，終於去到神盾局總部。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/e6/00/68/e600680ae6e456eefa73b1b41bb2732e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2Fe6%2F00%2F68%2Fe600680ae6e456eefa73b1b41bb2732e.jpg&h=a6fa1ddc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n坐電梯，到某一層，到某間房，開門入內，入面見到有成棚人開緊會。<br />\n有男有女，有老有嫩。<br />\n<br />\n我雙淫眼一野掃過去，果然見到左邊有正野：<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/1c/f0/ec/1cf0ec5774c7e07c2e3359f046be9f47.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F1c%2Ff0%2Fec%2F1cf0ec5774c7e07c2e3359f046be9f47.jpg&h=58bff467&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n嗯嗯，床前明月光，疑是地上霜，好詩好詩。<br />\n<br />\n再掃埋去右邊，屌你老味，又有正菜：<br />\n<img src=\"https://reellifebygrace.files.wordpress.com/2016/09/wanda-maximoff.jpg?w=700\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Freellifebygrace.files.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F09%2Fwanda-maximoff.jpg%3Fw%3D700&h=68dee445&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n嗯嗯，香港還是有希望的。<br />\n<br />\n我睇女睇到眼珠幾乎跌落地之際，我 feel 到身後有人行過，而且我個淫鼻索到有髮香，於是回頭一瞄：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/WAqmJblMO__SmocPdpwZql7pfk8=/62x0:1862x1350/1200x800/filters:focal(62x0:1862x1350)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/49563957/emily-vancamp.0.0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.vox-cdn.com%2Fthumbor%2FWAqmJblMO__SmocPdpwZql7pfk8%3D%2F62x0%3A1862x1350%2F1200x800%2Ffilters%3Afocal%2862x0%3A1862x1350%29%2Fcdn.vox-cdn.com%2Fuploads%2Fchorus_image%2Fimage%2F49563957%2Femily-vancamp.0.0.jpg&h=61101d5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屌，都嗒得杯落喎<br />\n<br />\nOK，上飛機前，我話我好撚唔情願。<br />\n我而家收返我講過嘅說話。"},{"pid":"59c7256df3249c08ed317d38d4616baf5818e4fd","tid":1133757,"uid":65030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T14:00:17.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"e20bc7b3637f1743ceb13c50b1d988d5262a0476","tid":1133757,"uid":205125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T14:25:55.000Z","msg":"LM 支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa91286ffedbc19037f7649f33cf1f607ce0354b","tid":1133757,"uid":207702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T19:29:41.000Z","msg":"加速<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db4ce409874a8ecd78bc9f4e9e198cc6c52b0319","tid":1133757,"uid":217162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T19:51:10.000Z","msg":"太早入黎"},{"pid":"e9bec56d8789f1cf170705c89acd6eaac80724eb","tid":1133757,"uid":87507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T19:51:31.000Z","msg":"會唔會已經爛尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5732054935830dc7fb87813f302de3e2a0ccf59c","tid":1133757,"uid":124262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T19:55:03.000Z","msg":"lm支持"},{"pid":"e3f14a3e2d2b952bc37ea89cc64f5bde6128a6d7","tid":1133757,"uid":242386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T19:57:52.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"83073abac0d91ef63586dfb1a685e3e996313e24","tid":1133757,"uid":8313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T20:00:29.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"ab50719d8cc17b22f39cf981107cb99100222556","tid":1133757,"uid":75556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T05:17:06.000Z","msg":"等爛尾"},{"pid":"be6fede29805709da3b8c3678a4efe95149f467f","tid":1133757,"uid":26711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T08:34:31.000Z","msg":"尾已爛"},{"pid":"4ea1834ad9db42e1429634e6eec02261012a96b8","tid":1133757,"uid":8578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T02:45:41.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"4672c763a11b6a58dfcaac3476190dbe185380dc","tid":1133757,"uid":8578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T02:46:02.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"bcc6a1fddf22985ad2e7e20f02f1034329b32c88","tid":1133757,"uid":29513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T02:47:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61fe92de10a753decbad7fd5d854530303ebb7dd","tid":1133757,"uid":47279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T02:51:53.000Z","msg":"用英文寫啦on9"}]}